OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764274
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,FFamily members of a police officer who
OL,7,Fdrowned when he fell into Bristol
OL,8,Fharbour say they'll never stop
OL,9,Ffighting for improved safety measures.
OL,11,FPc Rehaan Akhtar, 28, had been
OL,12,Fdrinking with friends in Bristol and
OL,13,Fwas last seen in the early hours of
OL,14,FNovember 23 last year.
OL,16,FDuring an inquest into his death, Avon
OL,17,FCoroner's Court heard Mr Akhtar did
OL,18,Fnot return to the youth hostel where
OL,19,Fhe was staying and was reported
OL,20,Fmissing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,FHis body was recovered by divers from
OL,7,FBristol harbourside on the morning of
OL,8,FNovember 24.
OL,10,FSpeaking after the inquest, Mr
OL,11,FAkhtar's sisters, Meena and Rabia
OL,12,FNajmi, said they did not want another
OL,13,Ffamily to suffer the same tragedy.
OL,15,F"It is quite disappointing to hear
OL,16,Fthat there's going to be no kind of
OL,17,Fdrastic safety measures put in place
OL,18,Fto prevent it happening in future,"
OL,19,FMeena Najmi said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"There's nothing to say it's not going
OL,7,Fto happen again. We are just confused
OL,8,Fas to how many more times it's got to
OL,9,Fhappen before safety measures are put
OL,10,Fin place.
OL,12,F"At Swansea Marina there was a lot of
OL,13,Fdeaths with people falling into the
OL,14,Fwater. It's quite a busy area with a
OL,15,Flot of pubs, bars and clubs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"Once the railings were introduced it
OL,7,Fstopped. We have not had that kind of
OL,8,Fissue there since and I think if
OL,9,FBristol were to take that on board, it
OL,10,Fcould prevent this happening in
OL,11,Ffuture."
OL,13,FShe added: "We will continue to push,
OL,14,Fwe will continue to fight, to try and
OL,15,Fpush for some safety measures because
OL,16,Fwe don't want any other families to
OL,17,Fhave to go through what we've been
OL,18,Fthrough.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]uD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"It could have been avoided if the
OL,7,Fright safety measures were in place,
OL,8,Fin our opinion."
OL,10,FThe inquest heard that on the day he
OL,11,Fdisappeared Mr Akhat had started
OL,12,Fdrinking with friends in the afternoon
OL,13,Fand the group had carried on until
OL,14,Fafter midnight,
OL,16,FIn a written statement, one of his
OL,17,Ffriends on the trip - Corey Griffiths
OL,18,F- said they all drunk around eight
OL,19,Fpints of lager, two cocktails and a
OL,20,FJagerbomb during visits to several
OL,21,Fpubs and bars in Bristol.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,FAt the end of the evening, Mr
OL,7,FGriffiths said that while three of
OL,8,Ftheir friends remained out to get some
OL,9,Ffood, he and Mr Akhtar returned to
OL,10,Fwhere they were staying.
OL,12,F"I walked over the bridge with Rehaan
OL,13,Fand I remember talking and being on my
OL,14,Fphone," he said.
OL,16,F"I can't remember what I was doing on
OL,17,Fmy phone. Then I next recall being
OL,18,Finside the hostel trying to get the
OL,19,Fkey for the room as we only had one
OL,20,Fkey between the three of us.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@GO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"I thought in the morning that Rehaan
OL,7,Fhad been with me when I checked in,
OL,8,Fbut clearly that wasn't correct.
OL,10,F"In terms of how Rehaan was
OL,11,Fpresenting, we had all been drinking
OL,12,Fall day, and I was the same.
OL,14,F"Rehaan was drunk but there was not a
OL,15,Fparticular moment I noticed him
OL,16,Fsuddenly become more drunk or anything
OL,17,Flike that. He appeared the same as the
OL,18,Frest of us."
OL,20,FA post-mortem examination found Mr
OL,21,FAkhtar had drowned.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,FToxicology tests show that he had a
OL,7,Fblood alcohol reading of 260mg per
OL,8,F100ml of blood ` meaning he was the
OL,9,Fequivalent of three times the drink-
OL,10,Fdrive limit.
OL,12,FPathologist Dr Karin Denton said the
OL,13,Flevel of alcohol Mr Akhtar had
OL,14,Fconsumed would have likely affected
OL,15,Fhis speech and ability to walk.
OL,17,F"It is therefore likely that
OL,18,Fintoxication contributed to the fall
OL,19,Finto the water of the harbour," she
OL,20,Fsaid in her report.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"The water is very cold at that time
OL,7,Fof year."
OL,9,FA police investigation found no third
OL,10,Fparty involvement in his death.
OL,12,FOfficers had recovered CCTV evidence
OL,13,Fshowing someone matching the
OL,14,Fdescription of Mr Akhtar "fall into
OL,15,Fthe river from the jetty dock in front
OL,16,Fof the Arnolfini (arts centre)".
OL,18,FDr Peter Harrowing, area coroner for
OL,19,FAvon, recorded a conclusion of
OL,20,Faccidental death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@IO]vD@ZOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"I've heard evidence that he was in
OL,7,FBristol with friends, visited various
OL,8,Festablishments and was consuming
OL,9,Falcohol for a number of hours that
OL,10,Fday," the coroner said.
OL,12,F"He went to return to his
OL,13,Faccommodation, but for some reason `
OL,14,Fperhaps becoming disorientated ` he
OL,15,Fthen sadly falls into the water
OL,16,Fdrowning."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@EO]tD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,FThe coroner did not make a prevention
OL,7,Fof future deaths report after hearing
OL,8,Fevidence from the Bristol harbour
OL,9,Fmaster about ongoing improvements to
OL,10,Fwater safety.
OL,12,FDavid Lockwood told the court that the
OL,13,Fharbour was regularly inspected and
OL,14,Fthere had been improvements to
OL,15,Fsignage, rescue equipment and re-
OL,16,Frouting a cycle path.
OL,18,F"A blanket solution, for example
OL,19,Ffencing the whole estate, is not
OL,20,Frecommended as an acceptable or
OL,21,Fpractical control method," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"Work is ongoing to provide and
OL,7,Fmaintain aids to those who fall into
OL,8,Fthe water, such as grab chains and
OL,9,Fladders.
OL,11,F"The city remains committed to doing
OL,12,Feverything reasonably practicable to
OL,13,Fenhance safety, informed by evidence,
OL,14,Fpartnership working and findings and
OL,15,Fformal investigations when available."
OL,17,FMr Akhtar, from Llanelli, was a
OL,18,Fconstable with South Wales Police. He
OL,19,Ffirst joined the force as a police
OL,20,Fcommunity support officer (PCSO).
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,FHe was a PCSO in Cardiff from October
OL,7,F2021 and became a Pc based in Swansea
OL,8,Fin September 2023.
OL,10,FFollowing the inquest, Councillor
OL,11,FAndrew Brown, Chair of the Harbour
OL,12,FCommittee said: "My sincere
OL,13,Fcondolences go out to the families and
OL,14,Ffriends affected by the tragic death
OL,15,Fof PC Akhtar.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"Entering the open water of Bristol's
OL,7,Fharbour and other waterways presents
OL,8,Fsignificant risks. I urge everyone to
OL,9,Fstay away from the water's edge,
OL,10,Fparticularly if you have been drinking
OL,11,For are alone, and to look out for each
OL,12,Fother."
OL,14,FHe added: "There are several safety
OL,15,Ffeatures already in place around the
OL,16,Fharbour including life rings, throw
OL,17,Flines, frequent emergency access
OL,18,Fpoints and signs warning of the water
OL,19,Fhazards.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778764275
OL,3,CFamily of officer who drowned say
OL,4,Cthey'll never stop fighting for justice
OL,6,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,7,FBristol Business Improvement District
OL,8,F(BID) and emergency services to raise
OL,9,Fawareness of the risks around open
OL,10,Fwater and to help keep people safe
OL,11,Facross the city centre."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
